{"tid":174113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為淋病站台學生 原來係黃絲/本土學生？","createTime":"2017-03-26T14:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T03:46:28.000Z","uid":83052,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5faf1e2a0480401c2ba0b7531c4696c67c2fd279","tid":174113,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T14:34:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170326&amp;guid=56483501&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170326%26guid%3D56483501%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=1d0416ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170326%26guid%3D56483501%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=3209206e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170326&amp;guid=56483501&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n識時務者魏駿傑<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d59a30d3076a0de0366a5aa43a967b5efb7012","tid":174113,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T14:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bcc3560f97825bcbcba1246ccfc3d8f753614c2","tid":174113,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T14:38:24.000Z","msg":"做卧底既野<br />\n你識條鐵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4229308f94c80e41abb09a08183b2d02785b4d5e","tid":174113,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T14:40:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做卧底既野<br />\n你識條鐵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能真係忍辱負重"},{"pid":"334b9370d8eb86435868e82b3f22fa6e8893c1b2","tid":174113,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T14:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a80de025a211fcedeac846bdfca3134cb4674d3","tid":174113,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T14:41:23.000Z","msg":"仲有學生運動無畏無懼嘅前學民仔<br />\n<br />\n【前學民仔現身林鄭競選辦慶功宴】<br />\n<br />\n放棄原則的那張嘴面，實在十分可怕。我常告戒自已，千萬不要成為自已曾經討厭的人。<br />\n<br />\n副本抄送：林鄭月娥競選辦公室Benson Luk及Marco Li<br />\n<br />\n《是日新聞：為奶媽站台學生 原來係黃絲？》<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170326/56483501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170326%2F56483501&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=8cf20774\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170326%2F56483501&h=8d6fbc53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170326/56483501</a><br />\n在林鄭今天的慶功宴上，也有前「學民仔」的身影。與林鄭一起舉勝利手勢合照的李俊霖，今個學年一度參選教育大學學生會，在競選內閣擔任會長，今年一月卻以經常到外國為由退莊。有學民思潮前成員向《蘋果》確認，李曾在金鐘參與佔領運動。<br />\n李俊霖2012年以學民思潮義工身份接受《蘋果》訪問，斥梁振英玩弄語言偽術、任人唯親。他當時形容中學生已醒覺，「就好似沉睡嘅獅子，呢股力量開始抬頭，可以影響另一群人，左右政府政策」，呼籲市民參與2013年元旦遊行。<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【為正策士集梁粉奶粉 包括前學民仔李俊霖】<br />\n2017年壹仔報導<br />\n<br />\n成員則包括前學民仔李俊霖（Marco），他亦被盛傳正為林鄭助選。據了解，李俊霖是當年被學民唯一一個革退的成員，「Marco係好想上位嘅人，成日都喺學民玩權鬥。一三年學民喺街頭公民抗命，前面啲人喺度瞓馬路，佢喺後面叫人走，因為佢自己唔想俾人拉。Benson就收留呢啲喺社運圈上唔到位嘅人。」一名前學民成員說。 <br />\n<br />\n林鄭今次參選來得非常倉促，主因是梁振英忽然被北京通知連任無望。據了解，當日林鄭說重新考慮出選之時，陸瀚民亦「收到order」要幫林鄭埋班，包括找來前僱主、世聯顧問行政總裁麥黃小珍加入團隊，「Benson之前喺世聯做過，林鄭做發展局局長時，有幾個project就係同世聯合作，包括市區重建策略檢討，佢同林鄭一早已經識。」事實上，麥黃小珍是林鄭的大學同窗，外界一直指她是林鄭的公關大臣，但其實她也是被牽線而加入團隊，而陸就一直扮演中間人。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ce2017.appledaily.com.hk/articles/2_482921_0?EDM=EDITORIAL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fce2017.appledaily.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2_482921_0%3FEDM%3DEDITORIAL&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=43a282ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ce2017.appledaily.com.hk/articles/2_482921_0?EDM=EDITORIAL</a><br />\n<br />\n【90後新世代李俊霖：不倒梁國教必重來】<br />\n2012年蘋果訪問<br />\n<br />\n中六生李俊霖是學民思潮義工，佔領政總期間，他當司儀，帶領市民喊口號，也曾站在台上向母親道歉。李俊霖說，當師奶也對梁振英反感時，可見這政府有多不濟。近月中央政策組下令所有政府公職任命，都要知會全職顧問高靜芝，他們這班中學生也看穿梁用人唯親，「委任所有『梁粉』入局，所有政策都偏向梁振英一個人」。當這種政治審批伸延至校長、校監，全屬梁的「自己人」，「結果好簡單，學生嘅意見反映唔到，國民教育會捲土重來」。<br />\n<br />\n反國教運動後，李俊霖發現身邊多了同學對社會議題表達意見，包括新界東北發展及守護龍尾等；他以前會覺得社會上總有其他人代替自己發聲，但經過反國教一役，醒覺中學生的力量可以很大，再不是乳臭未乾被忽略的一群，「就好似沉睡嘅獅子，呢股力量開始抬頭，可以影響另一群人，左右政府政策」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20121228/18116268\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20121228%2F18116268&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=de9c3a02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20121228%2F18116268&h=83219c13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20121228/18116268</a><br />\n<br />\n相片來源：蘋果日報【獨家慶功宴】林鄭開香檳慶祝 奶粉爭住攬<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170326/56483087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170326%2F56483087&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=aecdb005\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170326%2F56483087&h=7ede15e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170326/56483087</a>"},{"pid":"217f4c0576f730ae55ed14eb6b55c7b5a7ae5fab","tid":174113,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"世界仔，投共最抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a73e