c=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 會唔會做滲透<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係就唔好打搞人"},{"pid":"0fcf66264553174cf464a4d3ef40f17bd0135dff","tid":174113,"uid":49609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T15:29:09.000Z","msg":"叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b87a6ad347e9187ef8da7b41d50fa7ae2723b6","tid":174113,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T15:33:05.000Z","msg":"邊個贏就join邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}